---
description: Frontend conventions for React + Ant Design
globs: ["frontend/src/**/*.{ts,tsx}"]
alwaysApply: false
---
- ALL theme values (colors, fonts) MUST come from antdTheme.ts via ConfigProvider — no hardcoded hex values in components.
- Colors: primary/accent Red #f05756, Orange #f68c45 as accents only. Header bar Black #232323. Content/sidebar Light BG #f7f6f4.
- Logo: dark backgrounds = gradient glyph + white wordmark. Light backgrounds = gradient glyph + Grey #525957 wordmark. NEVER black wordmark.
- Use Ant Design Skeleton while loading, Empty for empty states, notification for API success/error.
- All API calls via axios with JWT bearer token from AuthContext.
- Desktop-primary layout using Ant Design Layout + Row/Col grid — no fixed pixel widths.